column3: “Migraine pain comin on; nausea 6-7 when I medicated round 1930 or so. Takes bout 5 min to start working. Pain/nausea gone. No anxiety/paranoia (a must for me). Body high allowed me to eat dinner. Head high social & strong, very nice. High lasted 3 + hours, very nice for a Sativa dominant. Highly recommend for daytime use for pain/nausea! :-)”

“My first foray into hybrids as I usually go for the indicas.  I have PTSD and anxiety and didn't want to make that worse.  This is fab.  Sweet smelling, smooth, and a nice, let's get moving buzz.  I cleaned the house! :)  Good focus too.”

“An Indica leaning hybrid, this Super hybrid is a culmination of four strains, None of which tastes like peaches. Peaches and Cream tastes Peachy Keen though, so allow yourself some time on a nice Summer day to eat some Chronic Ice Cream with some Peaches and Cream Marijuana.”

“This strain is as great as it’s been hyped up to be, in my opinion. The bud I got is covered in trichomes and weighed 2.5 grams. It smells amazing and the smoke was smooth as hell, I hardly coughed at all. Huge selling point for me since I have a rough time smoking flower because of how harsh it is on my throat. Peaches and cream is the perfect name for it too, because you just feel so... peaches and cream. My best f...”
“Euphoric is an understatement. Great long lasting happy feelings and creative uplifted mood. Great to bring you out of s funk.”
“one of my top 5. great smell, taste, and high. long high at that.”

“Peaches and cream slips it's way in pretty quick so much so that you don't even know it hit you, you're just smacked, you can def taste like a spicy mint and a fruity sweet, and music sounds just about amazing makes you energetic to do work or maybe after a long day for a party is highly recommended makes you so happy”

“Migraine pain 6-7; nausea 6 when I medicated round 2000 or so. Takes bout 5 min to start working. Pain/nausea gone. No anxiety/paranoia (a must for me). Body high saved my @$$ from going to the ER! Head high energetic & creative. Tastes sweet like citrus to me. High lasted over 2 hours; not bad. Highly recommend for daytime use for pain/nausea! :-)”

“I love this for daytime use. It's not to much that I cannot function at work but still gives me the head change I look for when medicating. The taste though, is the main reason I have chosen this product more than once at the dispensary.  I received mine at:

🍑  The Verdes Foundation 🍑

Office Address:
6005 Coronado NE Suite A
Albuquerque, NM 87109
Office Hours:
Monday - Friday 10am-5:30pm
Saturday 10am - 4pm 
Phon...”
“PEACHY SKREECHY BAT SITTING PRETTY QUEEFY CAT...BLORTZ”

“This one is such a peachy dream! 🍑  🥛 🤤 Vaped some of this and it’s mostly a mellow peach flavor with a smooth aftertone.  Definitely not too creamy at all, this is a great afternoon hybrid for social gatherings or just chilling 😎. If you want a slightly sativa dom hybrid with a mellow peach flavor, than this is for you. 

My True Rating: 4.6 
-BPop6”

“Very nice as a live resin concentrate. Taste like a minty peach that immediately fills your mouth but leaves a subtle sweet aroma lingering on your tastebuds. High comes on smoothly and then next thing you realize your sitting on the toilet making your first review cause ya boy smacked”
“slight mdma come on quickly fades to a calming content indica dominant high.”
“I was able to get deep into thought and contemplation on this strain, incredible sativa.”
“smell and taste is amazing and the high is great”
“Lovely strain. Super relaxed. This is what old English men smoke. I feel like a raisin rn.”
“Can I start off by saying, Holy Shit! I love GTH but this is AWESOME... light floral with undertones of spiciness. Can someone do the Rick Flair.”
“Lovely strain. Super relaxed. This is what old English men smoke. I feel like a raisin rn.”
“really does smell like peaches”
“Very smooth and sweet with a solid effect on pain, stress and anxiety. Very good flavor and smell.”

“Peaches & Cream, from Verdes! Another knock out from Verdes. This strain was perfect on V-Day, a nice after work hybrid that gives you a heady feel. Terrific for the wind down on the day but this strain can also getSmooth, peachy & sweet tasting with the undertone of spice is the unique taste this flower had.  Quality flower from a quality dispensary.”
“Love how this bud looks”
“It’s super tasty as the name implies and I’ve found it acceptable for all day use. Perfect strain for a chill summer.”

“This is absolutely fabulous. Taste great and very smooth. I suffer from PTSD and chronic pain with my back and neck. Pain was gone and this incredible strain left me feeling very relaxed focused and stress free.  One of my favorites. My good feeling lasted almost all day. Love this!”
“This is great to calm my anxiety down, while still motivating me to get up and get things done. It is also great at elevating my mood!”

“Love at first sniff. Very strong peachy scent, makes the mouth water a bit. High comes on strong within a few minutes. Strong pressure around the eyes, mind feels refreshed and creative, body feels relaxed but I'm ready to go do some hiking. Smoked a 1/2 gram pre roll and I feel it's the perfect dosage of meds to ease the mind and carpe-diem.”
“Potent mixture of head and body rush.”

“Omg what a bus to have!!!! 
The smell and taste is out of this world....you won't be disappointed.”
“One of my favorite strains. Peaches and Cream delivers a nice Anxiety Free" high with a nice calming effect. Perfect for relaxing
“Very nice strain, one of my personal favorites!”

“It's very pleasant to smoke both smooth and sweet. The buds actually do smell like peaches when you bust open a sealed bag not a super pungent or skunk smell at all and the appearance of the weed isn't all that outstanding to make it look like a top grade smoke. Very typical looking dispensary quality Hybrid strain. The label says it is not 70 sativa 30 indica as I often see of this strain but I purchased some that w...”

“One of my all time favorite strains. Super skunky and cheesey and definitely not for the unseasoned smoker. A little goes a long way. A very good strain for alleviating pain,stress,depression,etc. does have the typical indica effects, tastes amazing. A must try if you haven't!”
“Amazing strain! Smells amazing! Just like peach cobbler or a peach dessert. Great sweet and pungent flavor. High is nice and thought provoking while relaxing at the same time. A+ strain.”

“This is absolutely fabulous. Taste great and very smooth. I suffer from PTSD and chronic pain with my back and neck. Pain was gone and this incredible strain left me feeling very relaxed focused and stress free.  One of my favorites. My good feeling lasted almost all day. Love this!”
“It’s super tasty as the name implies and I’ve found it acceptable for all day use. Perfect strain for a chill summer.”
“This is a great strain. The only reason I give it a 4 is because I got lost while driving and started becoming trippy. Besides that I felt great! Very good taste and fruity thick smoke.”
“Nice and soothing.”
“yummy :) nice and relaxing...”
“Absolutely love this strain! Smells amazing, tastes great and gives a great cerebral uplifting high while relaxing stress of the mind and soreness of body.... Reminds me of a creamy trainwreck”
“Enjoyed this strain had a very heady high but felt totally relaxed”
“Purchased some buds from SoFresh at Oregon's Finest. Very indica dominant, perfect for pain and stress. Very relaxing and euphoric high, while also providing deep muscle relaxation.”

“I had this stuff back a year ago and it was some of the most delicious herb i've had. it was cured when i picked it up and was a little orangey-red in colour but it was awesome stuff. 5/5 totally recommended guysú”
“Love me some peaches and cream!  Nice hybrid that makes me want to move around.  Tasty just like it sounds.  Found myself in a motivated state.  Highly recommend pun intended.”
“love this strain. super smooth! one of my favorites to smoke after work.”
“One of my favorites! Very calming high with no anxiety. Would highly recommend to anyone!”
“This is hands-down my absolute favorite strain. Relaxes me fast, which cuts down on my back pain. No paranoia at all. And it smells amazing. Just perfect.”
“Amazing taste”
“It was ok. It tastes like a dream, and the high was good, but I was expecting something a little harder hitting.”
“Very intense high. I was high from a few hits, and then got extremely tired. One of the best strains for insomnia.”
“one of my favorite strains in world”

“Picked up an eight from Nectar in Portland of some amazing Peaches and Cream grown by the legendary TJ's Organics. Awesome taste and a very long and euphoric high, some of the best bud I've found in PDX in a little while!”
“Good intense high, very sleepy and made me very depressed towards the end, wouldn't pick this at my main strain to smoke, but nice here and there.”
